def main():
    N = int(input())
    A = list(map(int, input().split()))
    ans = 0

    for i in range(N):
        ans = max(ans, A[i] - A[i-1])

    print(ans)


if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()

def main():
    N, M = map(int, input().split())
    AC_count = 0
    penalty_count = 0
    for i in range(M):
        p, s = input().split()
        if s == "AC":
            AC_count += 1
            penalty_count += int(p)
    print(AC_count, penalty_count)


if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()
